"藍到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5751a227f2975f8392187a2e21d8078a4a7aee64","tid":2413554,"uid":5320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T21:19:26.000Z","msg":"很得輝"},{"pid":"d28f98a993a6e8d9e63f46c7357ad74eb1da0fb9","tid":2413554,"uid":152298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T21:20:18.000Z","msg":"kfc<br />\n一係死咸<br />\n一係乾哂<br />\n一係燶哂<br />\n無食好多年<br />\n十幾年前還可以火喉控制仲未失控"}]}